items.title: Awesome Dart
items.content_text:
### Cross-platform development

*   [universal\_io (⭐99)](https://github.com/terrier989/universal_io) - *dart:io* that also works in the browser.
*   [universal\_html (⭐0)](https://github.com/terrier989/universal_html) - *dart:html* that also works in the VM/Flutter.

items.title: Awesome Machine Learning
items.content_text:
### Julia / General-Purpose Machine Learning

*   [Flux](https://fluxml.ai/) - Relax! Flux is the ML library that doesn't make you tensor

### Julia / Natural Language Processing

*   [Word Tokenizers (⭐99)](https://github.com/JuliaText/WordTokenizers.jl) - Tokenizers for Natural Language Processing in Julia
*   [Embeddings (⭐81)](https://github.com/JuliaText/Embeddings.jl) - Functions and data dependencies for loading various word embeddings
*   [Languages (⭐54)](https://github.com/JuliaText/Languages.jl) - Julia package for working with various human languages
*   [WordNet (⭐34)](https://github.com/JuliaText/WordNet.jl) - A Julia package for Princeton's WordNet

### Julia / Misc Stuff / Presentations

*   [DataDeps (⭐154)](https://github.com/oxinabox/DataDeps.jl) - Reproducible data setup for reproducible science.

items.title: Awesome Android
items.content_text:
### GUI

*   [MaterialProgressBar (⭐2.2k)](https://github.com/zhanghai/MaterialProgressBar) - Material design ProgressBar with consistent appearance.

### GUI / Navigation

*   [Debug-Artist (⭐46)](https://github.com/BaristaVentures/android-debug-artist) - Debug menu to enable leakcanary, scalpel and others easy.

### Maps / ORM

*   [GLMap](https://globus.software) - Crossplatform offline vector map with MapCSS styling. Offline search and offline navigation are included.

### Utility / ORM

*   [Reactor (⭐39)](https://github.com/oky2abbas/reactor) - Reactor is a fast and secure key-value library for Android.

items.title: Awesome Wagtail
items.content_text:
### Apps / Widgets

*   [wagtail-instance-selector (⭐54)](https://github.com/ixc/wagtail-instance-selector) - A `ForeignKey` widget to create and select related items. Similar to Django's `raw_id_fields`.
items.content_html:
Apps / Widgets

  • wagtail-instance-selector (⭐54) - A ForeignKey widget to create and select related items. Similar to Django's raw_id_fields.
